Transfer ESSNH4 STORE2 Employee Via HRCI For Store On Web
    [Documentation]    Transfers the dynamic employee ESSNH4_STORE2 from STORE2 to STORE1 via HRCI file upload
    ...
    ...    This performs store transfer via HRCI with effective date as Day 1 of Current Week + 1.
    ...    The employee is transferred from STORE2 to STORE1.

    Log    🔄 Transferring ESSNH4_STORE2 from STORE2 to STORE1 via HRCI...    level=INFO

    # Get employee from suite variable
    ${essnh4_store2}    Get Dynamic Employee    ESSNH4_STORE2

    # Get store data for STORE1 (destination)
    ${store1_data}    Get Store Data

    # Get date configuration from environment
    ${date_format}    Get Config Value    SERVER_DF
    # Calculate transfer effective date as Day 1 of Current Week + 1 (1_0)
    ${transfer_effective_date}    Calculate Date From Week Day Offset    1_0    date_format=${date_format}
    # Calculate end date as Day 1 of Current Week + 2 (2_0)
    ${transfer_end_date}    Calculate Date From Week Day Offset    2_0    date_format=${date_format}

    # Get organizational data from STORE1
    ${staff_group_id}    Get System Value    HRBAStaffGroupId    NEWHIRE_STORE2_SG_1
    ${department_id}    Get System Value    HRBADepartmentId    NEWHIRE_STORE2_DEPT_1

    # Create HRCI store transfer data using default template with field overrides
    ${hrci_transfer_data}    Get Hrci Store Transfer Data
    ...    employee_id=${essnh4_store2}[employee_id]
    ...    effective_date=${transfer_effective_date}
    ...    end_date=${transfer_end_date}
    ...    home_store_id=${store1_data}[store_id]
    ...    home_department_id=${department_id}
    ...    home_staff_group_id=${staff_group_id}

    # Define file path for HRCI transfer file
    VAR    ${hrci_file_path}    web/Generated/HRCI_Store_Transfer_ESSNH4.txt

    # Login as SYSADMIN and upload HRCI file
    Login And Launch WFM Web App    user_key=SYSADMIN
    Perform HRCI Store Transfer Upload On Web    ${hrci_file_path}    ${hrci_transfer_data}
    Close Browser

    Log    ✅ Successfully transferred ESSNH4_STORE2 from STORE2 to STORE1, effective ${transfer_effective_date}    level=INFO

